punsReplies.message: - You are 'purr'fect!
- My god your fave is 'Cat'ostrophic!
- Hey i guess youre in a 'Pickel' welp I guess you have to 'Dill' with that.
- 'Donut' be sad! You're gonna have a 'Glazing' day!
- I gotta say, you're pretty 'Punny' for all these puns.
- What do they call so drinks in tins in Canada? 'Can-u-duh'!
- What animal can sing? 'Llama Del Rey'
- So, what do you wanna 'Taco'-bout?
- If you tell me any 'Egg' joke you're gonna 'crack me up' , so i guess the 'yolks' on you!
- I am a 'CANDY MAGICIAN' and i got a few 'TWIX' up my sleeves.
- Awh chin up friend! I be'leaf' in you!!
- Cute 'Bear' puns are so un'bear'able!
- How do mosters like their eggs? Terri-'fried'!
- If you get Helium (He) and times it by three (He)(He)(He) you get... 'Laughing gas'!
- Hey thanks for 'pudding' up with these puns!
- You're a slow tomato!.... try to 'ketchup'!
- What happens when peppers get cold? They become 'chilli peppers'.
- Knock* knock*... I just want to say you are a'door'able.
- Time flies like an arrow. But fruit flies like a banana!
- Wanna do a space party? Lets 'Planet'!
- 'Aloe' how are ya? Long 'Thyme' no see!
- What kind of shorts do clouds wear? 'Thunderwear'!
- 'Cheesy' puns 'Mac' me so happy!
- Why did the ghost go to the bar? For the 'Boooos'
